事业新平台。“就业要稳存量，还要扩增量。当前很多新业态新职业的出现，为大学生就业带来新的选择机会。民宿管家、网络带货主播、汉服妆造师等新职业出现，不仅引领了就业新风向，也开启了多元就业的尝试，有利于整个社会‘稳就业’目标的实现。”21世纪教育研究院院长熊丙奇说。 人民数据研究院发布《新青年 新机遇——新职业发展趋势白皮书》"},"attached_info":"Cj4IqZf+ocLP5sx6EAMaCDk3OTgzNTQ2II/EmaUGMAA4eEAacgk2MTA2NjIwOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1bff52e0fa49a9b2a606bed5dc27caf6_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1688678133.111831","card_id":"Q_298442489","target":{"id":298442489,"title":"爸爸带孩子是什么体验？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/298442489","type":"question","created":1539483476,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":81,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3143],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IqZf+ocLP5sx6EAMaCDI4NTk3MTkwINTOit4FMAA4UUAbcgkyOTg0NDI0ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1688678133.112104","card_id":"Q_519748828","target":{"id":519748828,"title":"有哪些你用了很久，体验感一直在线的厨房好物？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/519748828","type":"question","created":1646272867,"answer_count":41,"follower_count":96,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3519,8393,153736,246083,718485],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IqZf+ocLP5sx6EAMaCDc3NzgxNTk1IOPCgJEGMAA4YEAccgk1MTk3NDg4Mjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"46 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-84b95f62a8351194ba6e3cef8d1cf5d6_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","